title: Monthly Deaths from Lung Diseases in the UK
description:
Description
Three time series giving the monthly deaths from bronchitis,
emphysema and asthma in the UK, 1974–1979,
both sexes (ldeaths), males (mdeaths) and
females (fdeaths).
format:
P. J. Diggle (1990)
Time Series: A Biostatistical Introduction.
Oxford, table A.3
